The paper discusses the application of a decentralized architecture for industrial data analytics, which involves distributed computing and software engineering concepts. Therefore, cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.SE (Software Engineering) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper also involves concepts related to computer engineering (cs.CE), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in the context of data analytics.
